QuestData.Title: Smeed's Harnesses
QuestData.Description: Pardon me, young $r.$b$bI'm in need of a little help. I've just finished filling an order for harnesses that must be delivered right away.$b$bI'm a bit old for the trip, especially considering how dangerous things have become lately.$b$bWould you mind?$b$bThey need to go to Smeed, a goblin who lives just southeast of here.
QuestData.LogDescription: Nataka at Ghost Walker Post wants you to deliver Smeed's Harnesses to Smeed.
